$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
adjust_time_left

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
adjust_time_left -  Change the amount of time a player has left.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int adjust_time_left(int i)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - the amount of time units to change by
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the amount of time left

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/psoul.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Change the amount of time a player has left.  You call this after a command
has been executed to make it take more time.
.EP

